Come on, sweetheart.

01:39:52.438 --> 01:39:55.681
- No.
- Come away. Take her, Dallow.

01:39:55.816 --> 01:39:57.351
- Come on, sweetheart.
- No!

01:40:34.850 --> 01:40:36.339
What about the girl?

01:40:37.478 --> 01:40:38.967
Oh...

01:40:39.645 --> 01:40:41.637
Poor little kid.

01:40:43.192 --> 01:40:45.522
She thought he was in love with her.

01:40:46.859 --> 01:40:49.147
And was he?

01:40:49.280 --> 01:40:51.190
In love?

01:40:51.321 --> 01:40:53.152
What difference would that make?

01:40:53.283 --> 01:40:56.947
Well, it would show...
there was some good.

01:40:57.079 --> 01:40:58.113
Oh, Phil...

01:41:00.872 --> 01:41:02.612
I think it's a bleeding miracle

01:41:02.749 --> 01:41:07.286
that nature should have planted love
in every man jack of us, Ida.

01:41:09.380 --> 01:41:11.414
And every woman.

01:41:12.509 --> 01:41:14.840
Even though in some of us...

01:41:15.387 --> 01:41:17.797
...it's as useless as an appendix.

01:41:27.978 --> 01:41:29.970
Oh, I'm sorry, Ida.

01:41:30.982 --> 01:41:33.143
No, no, you're right, Phil.

01:41:41.116 --> 01:41:42.355
Let's celebrate.

01:41:44.661 --> 01:41:48.324
Well... Shall I get us
a bottle of champagne?

01:41:48.457 --> 01:41:50.491
Yes! Get us a bottle of champagne.

01:41:50.622 --> 01:41:52.363
And a room.

01:41:57.338 --> 01:42:00.377
Blimey. Talk about miracles.

01:42:05.470 --> 01:42:07.427
- It's expensive.
- I'll settle it.

01:42:07.556 --> 01:42:10.637
- No, a man likes to...
- Trust me, Phil.

01:42:12.352 --> 01:42:14.433
I know what a man likes.

01:42:47.592 --> 01:42:49.832
Go on, open it!

01:42:51.803 --> 01:42:53.714
I don't care what anyone says.

01:42:57.807 --> 01:42:59.422
You don't know a thing about love.

01:43:01.060 --> 01:43:04.303
How can you persist in this delusion,
child,

01:43:04.438 --> 01:43:06.928
after what he tried to do to you?

01:43:11.984 --> 01:43:14.068
I should have pulled the trigger.

01:43:18.867 --> 01:43:20.949
I don't want your absolution.

01:43:24.538 --> 01:43:26.701
I wanna be with Pinkie.

01:43:26.834 --> 01:43:30.245
- Go on, open it!
- What is going on over here?

01:43:31.042 --> 01:43:34.079
Get back to your beds, girls.

01:43:34.212 --> 01:43:37.331
The package is to be opened
in an orderly manner.

01:43:38.092 --> 01:43:40.254
